quran[15]{c,v,t,f}:
  37,91,"Nígbà náà, ó lọ sí ọ̀dọ̀ àwọn òrìṣà wọn. Ó sì sọ pé: “Ṣé ẹ kò níí jẹun ni?"
  37,92,"Kí ni ó ṣe yín tí ẹ kò sọ̀rọ̀?”"
  37,93,"Nígbà náà, ó dojú lílù kọ wọ́n pẹ̀lú ọwọ́ ọ̀tún (ó sì rún wọn wómúwómú)."
  38,70,"Kí ni wọ́n fi ránṣẹ́ sí mi bí kò ṣe pé èmi ni olùkìlọ̀ pọ́nńbélé.”"
  38,71,"(Rántí) nígbà tí Olúwa rẹ sọ fún àwọn mọlāika pé: “Dájúdájú Èmi yóò dá abara kan láti inú ẹrẹ̀."
  38,72,"Nígbà tí Mo bá ṣe é tó dọ́gba jálẹ̀ tán, tí Mo sì fẹ́ nínú atẹ́gùn ẹ̀mí tí Mo dá sínú rẹ̀, nígbà náà ẹ dojú bolẹ̀ fún un, kí ẹ forí kanlẹ̀ kí i.”"
  39,55,"Kí ẹ sì tẹ̀lé ohun tí ó dára jùlọ tí wọ́n sọ̀kalẹ̀ fún yín láti ọ̀dọ̀ Olúwa yín ṣíwájú kí ìyà náà tó wá ba yín ní òjijì, nígbà tí ẹ̀yin kò níí fura.”"
  39,56,"Nítorí kí ẹ̀mí kan má baà wí pé: “Mo ká àbámọ̀ lórí bí mo ṣe jáfara lórí àìtẹ̀lé àṣẹ Allāhu. Àti pé èmi wà nínú àwọn tó ń fi (ọ̀rọ̀ Rẹ̀) ṣe yẹ̀yẹ́.”"
  39,57,"Tàbí kí ó má baà wí pé: “Tí ó bá jẹ́ pé Allāhu fi ọ̀nà mọ̀ mí ni, dájúdájú èmi ìbá wà nínú àwọn olùbẹ̀rù (Rẹ̀).”"
  40,34,"Àti pé dájúdájú (Ànábì) Yūsuf ti tọ̀ yín wá ṣíwájú pẹ̀lú àwọn àlàyé ọ̀rọ̀ tó yanjú, ṣùgbọ́n ẹ̀yin kò yé wà nínú iyèméjì nípa ohun tí ó mú wá ba yín títí di ìgbà tí ó fi kú, tí ẹ fi wí pé: “Allāhu kò níí gbé Òjíṣẹ́ kan dìde mọ́ lẹ́yìn rẹ̀. Báyẹn ni Allāhu ṣe ń sọ ẹni tí ó jẹ́ aláṣejù, oníyèméjì nù.”"
  40,35,"Àwọn tó ń jiyàn nípa àwọn āyah Allāhu láìsí ẹ̀rí kan tí ó dé bá wọn. Ẹ̀ṣẹ̀ ńlá sì ni ní ọ̀dọ̀ Allāhu àti ní ọ̀dọ̀ àwọn tó gbàgbọ́ ní òdodo. Báyẹn ni Allāhu ṣe ń fi èdídí bo gbogbo ọkàn onígbèéraga, ajẹninípá.”"
  40,36,"Fir‘aon wí pé: “Hāmọ̄n, mọ ilé gíga fíofío kan fún mi nítorí kí èmi lè dé àwọn ojú ọ̀nà náà."
  41,13,"Tí wọ́n bá gbúnrí, sọ pé: “Èmi ń ṣèkìlọ̀ iná láti ojú sánmọ̀ irú iná láti ojú sánmọ̀ tó gbá ìjọ ‘Ād àti Thamūd mú fún yín ni.”"
  41,14,"Nígbà tí àwọn Òjíṣẹ́ wọn wá bá wọn níwájú wọn àti lẹ́yìn wọn,(wọ́n sọ) pé: “Ẹ̀yin kò gbọdọ̀ jọ́sìn fún ẹnì kan àyàfi Allāhu.” Wọ́n wí pé: “Tí ó bá jẹ́ pé Olúwa wa bá fẹ́ ni, ìbá sọ àwọn mọlāika kalẹ̀ (fún ìpèpè yìí). Dájúdájú àwa jẹ́ aláìgbàgbọ́ nínú ohun tí wọ́n fi ran yín níṣẹ́.” {1}",footnotes:1:[“níwájú wọn” túmọ̀ sí pé àwọn Òjíṣẹ́ Allāhu - kí ọlà Allāhu máa bá wọn - wá bá àwọn bàbá ńlá wọn, “lẹ́yìn wọn” sì túmọ̀ sí pé àwọn Òjíṣẹ́ Allāhu tún wá bá àwọn àrọ́mọdọ́mọ wọn lẹ́yìn ìparun àwọn bàbá ńlá wọn.]
  41,15,"Ní ti ìjọ ‘Ād, wọ́n ṣègbéraga ní orí ilẹ̀ láì lẹ́tọ̀ọ́. Wọ́n sì wí pé: “Ta ni ó lágbára jù wá lọ ná?” Ṣé wọn kò rí i pé dájúdájú Allāhu tí Ó ṣẹ̀dá wọn, Ó ní agbára jù wọ́n lọ ni? Wọ́n sì ń tako àwọn āyah Wa!"